Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.80,0:01:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十三話\N奪取光榮的頭銜 蒼紫的全新戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.46,0:01:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了京都 記得去白梁屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.36,0:01:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兒是我娘家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.66,0:02:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已寫信跟他們說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.20,0:02:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 啊妙 白梁屋 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.34,0:02:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是紅梁屋的分店啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.54,0:02:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都走了 真無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.94,0:02:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時無法見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們馬上就會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.95,0:02:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且帶著劍心一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.65,0:02:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保重嘍 禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.39,0:02:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.92,0:02:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.59,0:02:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.00,0:02:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小綾 小雀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠 玄齊老丈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.77,0:02:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易看完一個急診病人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.20,0:02:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差一點就趕不上了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.34,0:02:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.21,0:02:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不是你的一番話 我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.85,0:02:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於瞭解我的一片好意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.42,0:02:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好去吧 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.32,0:03:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰和禰彥可是代表我們哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.22,0:03:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可要把大家的心意\N傳達給劍心知道喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.30,0:03:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.77,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保重 保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.84,0:03:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們出發嘍 禰彥 去找劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.85,0:03:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要堅強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心沒讓我一起跟去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會後悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.17,0:04:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不是什麼累贅呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.48,0:04:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要證明給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.98,0:04:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在京都給我等著 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.85,0:04:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.63,0:04:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到還會回到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 他有刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道他不知道廢刀令嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.51,0:05:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太危險了\N根本就是太歲頭上動土嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在還敢帶刀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.08,0:05:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了自身安全 可別接近他呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.96,0:05:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向神谷薰道別了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.93,0:05:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 我失言了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從現在起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要並肩做戰對付志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可要好好配合喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並肩做戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.74,0:05:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保公卿被暗殺一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警部已忙得手忙腳亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.38,0:05:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以現在京都的事務\N就由我來負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.81,0:05:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛 擺那張臭臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.68,0:05:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正你來就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在出發還趕得上\N早上第一艘去大阪的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.79,0:05:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我還有話要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.13,0:05:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要 我要去東海道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擔心錢不夠嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船資 政府會出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄那幫人神出鬼沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好在船上突擊我們也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.61,0:06:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是那樣的話 船上沒有任何地方可躲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.98,0:06:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只會將無辜的人捲入廝殺之中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.65,0:06:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的想法仍是憧憬和平的浪人心態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.32,0:06:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該讓你再清醒一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.35,0:06:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我隨時都可配合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.06,0:06:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過唯獨這一次 我不想波及無辜的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.46,0:06:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正因如此 我才一個人出走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.94,0:06:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.50,0:06:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正有此意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但別忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.84,0:06:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄的眼線可是四處遍佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.55,0:06:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的行動全都在他掌握之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.85,0:06:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和志志雄的戰役早已展開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.32,0:06:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣帶著刀\N大家都會害怕而不敢靠近我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此就不會波及無辜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.36,0:07:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣是幕府末期的殘存者\N他在招喚我去京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.00,0:07:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前方是個什麼樣的對決 在等著我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.24,0:07:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小子 你竟敢在我面前帶刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可真大膽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.61,0:07:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.58,0:07:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.12,0:07:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.60,0:07:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉 最後我竟留在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.93,0:07:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被留在這看家 我…我到底在幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,門開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.14,0:07:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鑰匙在我這 怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是劍心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.02,0:07:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四乃森…蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.43,0:08:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊去哪兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.89,0:08:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…你還要索劍心的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.67,0:08:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…你知道的話\N我還希望你告訴我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.77,0:08:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不說 我就把你殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊去京都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.06,0:08:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是齊藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.03,0:08:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新撰組第三隊隊長 牙空派的名將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.51,0:08:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在竟成了政府的走狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.94,0:08:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 真不簡單 不愧是御庭派出身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說幕府末期的生還者\N又多了一人出現在東京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才來這兒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.92,0:09:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你隱密深山多時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.52,0:09:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓我告訴你 這些日子發生的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄真實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.61,0:09:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊或許會被志志雄打敗\N回不來也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.88,0:09:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.98,0:09:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也會去京都嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.45,0:09:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那個必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.08,0:09:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能打倒拔刀齊的只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.72,0:09:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真自大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.36,0:09:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但可別太自負啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.76,0:09:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟他說那麼多幹嘛 你這個流氓警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.70,0:09:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他可是只想殺劍心的 危險人物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.60,0:10:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂 我不說這些話 你早就被殺死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.31,0:10:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他年僅15就成了御庭派堂主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.05,0:10:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實是可用之材 就看會不會利用而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.15,0:10:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有同感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.52,0:10:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四乃森蒼紫 確實是可用之材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.83,0:10:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這小子 站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.34,0:10:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煩死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.08,0:10:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不想和任何人扯上關係啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.48,0:10:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.65,0:10:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.02,0:10:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這樣只是在搞環境破壞而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.09,0:10:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不算是什麼修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.13,0:10:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都到底在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.49,0:11:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等著看 我會打倒拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.59,0:11:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將光榮的花環插在你們的墓上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.83,0:11:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.47,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 說到那個女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次讓我看一眼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.90,0:11:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.21,0:11:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.87,0:11:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.18,0:11:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來得也太晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是四乃森…蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.02,0:11:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是偉大的志志雄陛下的使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊武隈四入道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.69,0:11:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你該感到高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.53,0:12:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄陛下蠻中意你的\N希望見你一面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.43,0:12:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像我們見志志雄陛下的機會\N一年還不知有沒有一次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.40,0:12:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可是給你賞臉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們回去跟他說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.81,0:12:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要見我的話 就自己來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們再破壞這些墓碑的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.78,0:12:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可饒不了你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即便志志雄也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會殺個遍甲不留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要以為有點伎倆就在那囂張 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說要殺我們 已經讓人很不爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.03,0:12:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還敢說要殺志志雄陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,膽敢愚弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄陛下的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.50,0:12:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不能讓他活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.41,0:12:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是長刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.14,0:12:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次敗給拔刀齊就換了武器啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.31,0:12:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你用什麼武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,單單一隻刀是無法對付我們的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.28,0:12:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四身一體術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.15,0:12:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刀鞘裏竟有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.09,0:12:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩把小太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.22,0:13:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫非…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.33,0:13:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太無情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓阿武隈四入道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.15,0:13:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連施展最得意的四身一體術的機會都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.52,0:13:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太刀二刀流…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.02,0:13:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是志志雄的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.52,0:13:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.22,0:13:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫瀨田宗次郎 志志雄陛下的隨身侍衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.36,0:13:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不愧被稱為天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.26,0:13:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起來聊一聊 如何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.60,0:13:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我可不打算跟在誰的門下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.54,0:13:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更不可能跟為了借他人之力\N而捨棄自己人的無情漢同夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.88,0:13:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你早就知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 明知他們被主人拋棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.45,0:14:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還毫不留情的將之趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.42,0:14:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也一樣無情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.26,0:14:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎 算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.76,0:14:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來 你們御庭派在明治維新時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.30,0:14:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫無用武之地就被滅門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.37,0:14:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那股挫折感一直留在心中吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕府末期 還有這一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.88,0:14:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在時代的變遷之中相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.31,0:14:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若再一次不戰而終的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不毀了御庭派的名聲嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心意改變的話 到京都來找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.27,0:15:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,堂主…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.24,0:15:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,堂主 我們從沒後悔\N身為御庭派的一份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.68,0:15:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.12,0:15:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真希望再度重回幕府末期和蒼紫堂主並肩作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們大家都和堂主是同樣的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.36,0:15:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕府末期 還有這一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.70,0:15:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在時代的變遷之中相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.60,0:15:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若再一次不戰而終的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.24,0:15:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不毀了御庭派的名聲嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.04,0:15:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.31,0:15:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要將光榮的花環獻給你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得早點動身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何啊 那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.69,0:15:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我蠻欣賞他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.72,0:15:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其是他殺人如斬草般的氣勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.79,0:15:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他好像沒有投靠的意願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.49,0:15:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他總有一天會派上用場的\N我要想想如何利用他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那下一步要怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.43,0:16:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先向千人斬的前輩打聲招呼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.91,0:16:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩 你是說拔刀齊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不覺得很有趣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.98,0:16:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從現在起 就是我的時代了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.49,0:16:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明明是走中山道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.43,0:16:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼還在山裏面啊 到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是北邊的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.20,0:16:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都在西邊 那麼應該在那兒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 朝京都出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.54,0:16:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（結果是越離越遠）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.75,0:16:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.85,0:16:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄一幫人已經夠麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.72,0:16:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在又多出了四乃森蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真令人擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠 你在幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.73,0:17:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（小惠擔心重重）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.24,0:17:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你看你看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.14,0:17:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露個臉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.31,0:17:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住宿請來小田屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.42,0:17:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來小田屋喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.75,0:17:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那位大俠 如何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.45,0:17:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝了 我還要趕路呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.02,0:17:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再急也沒用 現在走到箱根山都天黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.10,0:17:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你這住下會給你添麻煩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.47,0:17:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒錢是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.23,0:17:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大俠 要不要住宿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.17,0:17:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小美 別叫了 他沒銀子啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.01,0:17:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.18,0:17:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏帶著刀 還有人會理我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.56,0:18:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 好久沒有這樣宿營野地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.37,0:18:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家現在一定很氣我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被人怨恨也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.32,0:18:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會是志志雄一派吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.02,0:18:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是山賊就是強盜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.19,0:18:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不想和任何人有瓜葛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個小妮子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.57,0:18:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在還裝乖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你引誘我們的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.81,0:18:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家怕羞嘛 所以才戴著面紗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.38,0:19:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼嬌滴滴的聲音 真令人心醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.08,0:19:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你帶我們到這 可要好好陪我們玩一玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.62,0:19:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊 可是你們有錢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.59,0:19:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然有 還是剛從小田原家偷出來的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.80,0:19:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.03,0:19:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.07,0:19:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…戲就演到此了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.31,0:19:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快把錢全交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼 這小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.15,0:19:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是黃毛丫頭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.35,0:19:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為是什麼好貨色咧 畜牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這小鬼回去睡大覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.82,0:19:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王八烏龜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.20,0:19:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我哪裏像個小鬼 你神經病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.47,0:19:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.57,0:19:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也滿16歲了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.60,0:19:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別囂張了 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.94,0:19:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們膽大才去行竊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.94,0:20:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在連殺人都做得出來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.75,0:20:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.09,0:20:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動不動只會出手的人\N是無法捉到我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.33,0:20:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 也不過如此嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.50,0:20:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動點聲色 弄點小計謀 你們就上鉤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.57,0:20:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太遜了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真讓人吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.88,0:20:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早料到是劫財飛賊 但沒想到竟是個女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.62,0:20:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.29,0:20:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個路過的浪人
